data.description: Contemporary 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home located in Acworth, Cherokee County. This house includes a partially unfinished basement that can be easily converted into additional living space, along with a 2-car garage. The first floor features a 2-story living room with a fireplace, kitchen, dining room, laundry room, hall bath, and 2 secondary bedrooms. Upstairs, you will find the primary suite with a spacious walk-in closet, a large primary bathroom, and a loft overlooking the living room, ideal as an office or playroom. This home is in need of some tender loving care (TLC) and updates. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this property your own.
